00:39:42.566 --> 00:39:44.165 position:38.57%,start align:start size:30.95% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>(</c.mono_sans></c.white><c.white><c.mono_sans><i> sighing</i></c.mono_sans></c.white><c.white><c.mono_sans> )</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1065
00:39:44.165 --> 00:39:47.843 position:29.05%,start align:start size:51.90% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>during the occupation.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

