<c.white><c.mono_sans>You were there for Ghemor.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1081
00:40:29.672 --> 00:40:31.990 position:32.86%,start align:start size:42.38% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I owed it to him.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

